</EDIT> Please vote, I realy need to know! At me its NADA!
I tought I did something wrong when updating it, but it seemed I did not thanks to sL3Ak [quote="sL3Ak, post:1, topic:1866"]Ok I posted this on fagex, so here's a basic outlook on what has happened. I am a noob to these forums so don't flame or say shit about me.
Aryan may come to an end, for a period of time. As all co-ordinates have been changed, as the new Wilderness update had changed the co-ordinates, that Aryan has compiled inside it. Now basically, all that needs to be edited is, the co-ords within scripts, either that or tidy up the whole bot, which obviously will take alot of time, but i'm very sure some of the other communitys that dedicate their work to Aryan, and the editing of the bot.
Impsoft, and RsResources, will be the ones who'll end up fixing the bot and/or scripts, but until they do, there shall be no autoing what so ever.
On a side note- Jagex may find this time to ban your autoing accounts, as they'll notice that they don't seem to login, and with that they'll assume as checking the action within your account changing rapidly, then double track your IP back to your main account, may actually realise that you were autoing, and boom you're banned.
So watch out, remember when you auto use a proxy. Do not drop trade to your main. Remeber these things, it'll keep you safe.
